nodes.text: The Z-28 Skywing was a model of starfighter utilized by the Galactic Republic during the High Republic Era. Produced by Incom Corporation, the fighters had an arrowhead shape. The Republic was under direct control of a number of Skywings, while further squadrons of Skywings were owned by the member worlds of the Republic Defense Coalition. During the Battle of Kur, in which the Republic and the Jedi Order fought against the Nihil Tempest of Kassav Milliko, numerous Skywing squadrons were dispatched, with a number of the fighters being destroyed.
